    <text>
        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Calpurnius <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>nus et <expan><abbr>G</abbr><ex>aius</ex></expan> Vibius Quinti<lb break="no" n="2"/>lianus et <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Atti<supplied reason="lost">us<certainty locus="name" match="preceding-sibling::text()" cert="low"/> <gap reason="lost" extent="unknown" unit="character"/>u</supplied>s et <expan><abbr>M</abbr><ex>arcus</ex></expan> Verrius &amp;lt;G&amp;gt;eminus <lb n="3"/>solum tessellas<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>q</abbr><ex>ue</ex></expan> de suo strave</supplied>runt et donarunt
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Möglicherweise IIIIviri von Ossonoba oder magistri eines collegiums Dedikanten des Mosaikbodens. Inschriftfeld in Form eine tabula ansata. (B): AE 1981, Z.3: sol[um] tessellas [f(aciendum) curar]unt et donar[un]t; Lancha: Z.3: tessella s[traverunt dedicaver]unt. (B): Lancha, MCV: Z.3: tessella s[traverunt dedicaver]unt.</p>
            </div>
